{"talk":{"id":21033,"name":"Mary Maker: Why I fight for the education of refugee girls (like me)","description":"After fleeing war-torn South Sudan as a child, Mary Maker found security and hope in the school at Kenya's Kakuma Refugee Camp. Now a teacher of young refugees herself, she sees education as an essential tool for rebuilding lives -- and empowering a generation of girls who are too often denied entrance into the classroom. \"For the child of war, an education can turn their tears of loss into a passion for peace,\" Maker says.","slug":"mary_maker_why_i_fight_for_the_education_of_refugee_girls_like_me","recorded_at":"2018-06-09 00:00:00","published_at":"2018-08-15 15:01:13","updated_at":"2021-04-09 19:40:17","viewed_count":1194820,"emailed_count":0,"event":{"id":544,"name":"TEDxKakumaCamp"},"images":[{"image":{"size":"113x85","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/9602a5cbc39ef2cde1064b8da87c93f442d9a136_113x85.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"240x180","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/9602a5cbc39ef2cde1064b8da87c93f442d9a136_240x180.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"615x461","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/9602a5cbc39ef2cde1064b8da87c93f442d9a136_615x461.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"2400x1800","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/9602a5cbc39ef2cde1064b8da87c93f442d9a136_2400x1800.jpg"}}],"image_16x9":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/1333abb6987ff5a64f7f5b3e0c8d010db1fb9e26_2880x1620.jpg","media":{"internal":{"64k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/MaryMaker_2018X-64k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":8290702,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"180k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/MaryMaker_2018X-180k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":22974297,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"320k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/MaryMaker_2018X-320k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":40700150,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"450k":{"u